Trasana :<br>
<br>
&quot;Where else can you go at that ability range, and upgrade so many tanks at one time, and increase your DPS as much in a shot?&quot;<br>
<br>
The thing is, revamped sleepers is much like the old one <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  They even put ther warders back in - there is only a few items that no longer drop (i.e. SoD, monk shroud and the noam mask) - the primal are named prismatic, but they are essentialy the same. So guilds till can see the warders, they can still get their DPS weapons - the only thing they can't do is see the sleeper and get a few other items. <br>
