Sorry I’m late with the responses. After yesterday, I was tired of looking at this thread.<br>
<br>
To answer this, I simply say, But it’s perfectly alright for you to fuck someone else out of something they’ll never see. <br>
<br>
What sucks is that there really won’t be any repercussions from this that will really make a difference. Because we can’t actually see the other player on the other side of the screen, we shrug off things like respect and courtesy.<br>
<br>
Would it really have been a big deal if you would have just let him sleep? Would it have been really so hard for you just to pass on the last warder so that others could enjoy the experience? Your 15 minutes of something unseen completely soured the game for some here. If you want something unseen, find your way into the Plane of Time and take screen shots. There are certainly other parts of the game that people haven’t done yet that you could have been known for, AND RESPECTED for. <br>
<br>
I guess what pisses me off the most about this is that they’re not even apologizing for fucking it for the rest who won’t be able to see this. (Not that an apology will really make a difference… this can’t be changed.)<br>
<br>
Fact of the matter is, this won’t be forgotten, ever. (Not picking on this guild, but this proves my point) Peritus’ threads have exceeded the dreaded page 8 before and their shit happened a while ago. Somewhere down the line, someone will bring this up again and spurn another 20+ page thread. This will NEVER die…ever. <br>
<br>
Unless HS picks up, moves to a different server, and changes their name, this will haunt them for the rest of their gaming “careers”. <br>
<br>
Synd said:<br>
