I’m sorry, but when your guild stands for fucking over an entire server, dishonoring that pact, and your lack of compassion, concern, or sincerity for anyone else on your server, yeah… your leader’s opinion means shit. <br>
<br>
Anyone wearing the HS tag, in my eyes, is supporting this malicious message. Let’s face it, this is the ultimate KSing anyone has ever done…one of the worst crimes anyone can commit in the EQ Gaming World. And you and your guild condones this? Yeah…now there’s something to be proud of. Support that? Never and I hope the few good members left in your guild realizes this and does a /guildremove next chance they get to save what little reputation they have left.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> When your local football team makes it to the Superbowl <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
