<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> Now I know for sure you have completely lost all contact with reality and live in a dream world. Blood Cult, Diss, Oddy, OoD, Stormwind, Old Continent, Peritus all work together? Some of those guilds fucking dispise each other.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
