No, but now that your guild has moved to the bottom rung of the Guild Evolutionary Ladder, every single guild you mentioned would be civil enough to band together to make sure your gaming experience turns to shit.<br>
Plus, it should tell you something, that while although these guilds hate one another, they still had enough RESPECT for one another to leave The Sleeper alone. That places your guild on whale shit level, at the bottom of some deep oceanic cavern.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> See, it's all about the loot.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
