No it’s not you twit. Several people here have said it wasn’t. Some people it was, but not ALL of them. Besides, who are YOU to determine what people can get and not get? You arrogant pompus fucktard…If your dick was as big as your ego…..<br>
<br>
I suppose the only good thing now is that any guild that was held in poor respects, can now laugh, point a finger at HS and be thankful they’ve moved up nit picking food chain.<br>
