Skyhawk said:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> EQ, just like Life, is not always fair. Judging by your sig your lvl 51, so you should have learned that by now.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
