So that makes what they did right? I hate to break it to you, but being in a higher end guild doesn’t just mean that you get to see places and things that others will not. It means working in conjunction and harmony with everyone around you, from the Level 1 noob to the Revered 65 Vet. Whether you like it or not, there are people that look up to the higher end guilds so your reptuation travels with you. <br>
<br>
Life isn’t fair, you’re right…so the game people play to relax doesn’t have to mirror their lives. People play this game to escape the bullshit that life throws at them and the only thing they’ve done is remind them of the shit they escape from. <br>
<br>
What they did was tasteless… completely tasteless and I’m damn near ashamed to think I actually looked up to some of them, gaming wise. They raped this server of something they shall never get back. Congratufuckinglations.<br>
